{"id":7884,"date":"2025-12-29T15:03:34","date_gmt":"2025-12-29T08:03:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=7884"},"modified":"2025-12-30T09:30:08","modified_gmt":"2025-12-30T02:30:08","slug":"da-nhiem-corticoid-la-gi-cach-xu-ly-dung","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/da-nhiem-corticoid-la-gi-cach-xu-ly-dung\/","title":{"rendered":"Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00ec sao nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thuc-trang-da-nhiem-corticoid-tai-viet-nam-va-canh-bao-tu-thi-truong-my-pham\"><\/span><b>Th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng 10 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf da li\u1ec5u tuy\u1ebfn trung \u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam ghi nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ec7nh nh\u00e2n g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 da do l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng corticoid t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh. Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e1o c\u00e1o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh m\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u1edf nh\u00f3m ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef t\u1eeb 18\u201335 tu\u1ed5i. Theo nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a B\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Da li\u1ec5u Trung \u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n do m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c l\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u01a1n 60%, v\u00e0 do <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">d\u00f9ng thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ch\u1ee9a corticoid l\u00e0 11%<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7886\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7886\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7886 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-2.webp\" alt=\"L\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ec7nh nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb do d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m t\u1eafng cao\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7886\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ec7nh nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb do d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m t\u0103ng cao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m tr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, kem tr\u1ed9n, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a \u201ctr\u1eafng nhanh\u201d, \u201ch\u1ebft m\u1ee5n c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c\u201d, \u201cda m\u1ecbn ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y\u201d. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a corticoid m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p corticoid v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ng sinh v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m bong da, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean nh\u00e3n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ban \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea5y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh, da m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn, l\u00e0n da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 y t\u1ebf c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, g\u00e2y t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m chi ph\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ec7nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng: Corticosteroid b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i da b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 06\/2011\/TT-BYT c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 Hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ASEAN. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a Corticosteroid \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng thu\u1ed1c c\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 \u00fd t\u0103ng li\u1ec1u v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1eeba b\u00e3i.\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-nhiem-corticoid-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef chu\u1ea9n trong y khoa. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch g\u1ecdi chung c\u1ee7a t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do <\/span><b>s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng corticoid t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, kem b\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i da kh\u00f4ng theo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh y t\u1ebf. Corticoid l\u00e0 nh\u00f3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ec7nh da li\u1ec5u nh\u01b0 b\u1ec7nh v\u1ea3y n\u1ebfn, b\u1ea1ch bi\u1ebfn \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, ch\u00e0m, vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba, h\u1eb9p bao quy \u0111\u1ea7u, vi\u00eam da do x\u1ea1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea5p t\u00ednh, lichen planus, lichen simplex chronicus, lupus ban \u0111\u1ecf d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u0129a, vi\u00eam da m\u00e3n t\u00ednh v\u00e0 r\u1ee5ng t\u00f3c t\u1eebng m\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi d\u00f9ng sai c\u00e1ch ho\u1eb7c l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng, corticoid g\u00e2y ra h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u00ean c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7887\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7887\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7887 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-3.webp\" alt=\"Corticoid th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd v\u1ec1 da\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7887\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Corticoid th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd v\u1ec1 da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ede da b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, corticoid l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf, gi\u1ea3m ng\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhanh. Nh\u01b0ng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a nguy\u00ean b\u00e0o s\u1ee3i, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p collagen v\u00e0 elastin, khi\u1ebfn da m\u1ecfng, y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a da b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m, l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch l\u0169y theo th\u1eddi gian, th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf qua \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00ec bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bieu-hien-da-nhiem-corticoid-va-phan-loai-muc-do\"><\/span><b>Bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y theo th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 corticoid v\u00e0 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n s\u1edbm, c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn v\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7889\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7889\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7889 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-5.webp\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda da b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-5.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-5-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-5-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-5-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7889\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda da b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ede m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eb9, da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ecfng h\u01a1n, d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ecf khi g\u1eb7p n\u00f3ng, \u00e1nh n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9. Da c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch, n\u00f3ng r\u00e1t nh\u1eb9, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 \u00edt bong tr\u00f3c. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a corticoid v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng da \u0111ang ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u00edch nghi. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng teo da v\u00e0 gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7888\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7888\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7888 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-4.webp\" alt=\"Da s\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam \" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7888\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Da s\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ede m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 trung b\u00ecnh, da xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch r\u00f5, \u0111\u1ecf k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Da bong tr\u00f3c t\u1eebng m\u1ea3ng nh\u1ecf, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c n\u00f3ng r\u00e1t t\u0103ng l\u00ean. Khi ng\u01b0ng corticoid, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t vi\u00eam, n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n li ti ho\u1eb7c s\u1ea9n vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7890\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7890\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7890 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-6.webp\" alt=\"Da gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch b\u00f9ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-6.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-6-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-6-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-6-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7890\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Da gi\u00e3n mao m\u1ea1ch b\u00f9ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ede m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1eb7ng, da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, l\u1ed9 mao m\u1ea1ch d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf lan t\u1ecfa, k\u00e8m theo m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam da d\u1ea1ng rosacea. Da m\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng, kh\u00f3i b\u1ee5i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1y. \u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-nguyen-nhan-dan-den-da-nhiem-corticoid\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 <\/span><b>s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a corticoid kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c pha tr\u1ed9n th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng corticoid m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 <\/span><b>t\u1ef1 \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i da ch\u1ee9a corticoid<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> theo l\u1eddi m\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o, d\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ed1c c\u0169 ho\u1eb7c b\u00f4i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n th\u1eddi gian ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p d\u00f9ng corticoid cho m\u1ee5n, n\u00e1m ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam da nh\u1eb9 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00e2m l\u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da nhanh, thi\u1ebfu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 bu\u00f4ng l\u1ecfng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m gia t\u0103ng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-nhan-biet-san-pham-co-va-co-nguy-co-chua-corticoid\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9a corticoid<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 nhanh trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn. Da tr\u1eafng b\u1eadt t\u00f4ng, h\u1ebft m\u1ee5n ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-khong-nhan-mac-tron-tay-ruou-thuoc-gia-truyen\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng nh\u00e3n m\u00e1c tr\u1ed9n tay, r\u01b0\u1ee3u thu\u1ed1c gia truy\u1ec1n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7902\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7902\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7902 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-13.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kem tr\u1ed9n r\u01b0\u1ee3u thu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f4ng\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-13.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-13-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-13-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-13-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7902\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kem tr\u1ed9n r\u01b0\u1ee3u thu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f4ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb nghi\u1ec7n corticoid n\u1eb7ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a kem tr\u1ed9n. Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng l\u00ean livestream \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ee7 lo\u1ea1i kem v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i thau l\u1edbn tr\u1ed9n nh\u01b0 \u201cl\u00e0m b\u00e1nh\u201d, thu h\u00fat h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem t\u00ean facebook, youtube hay tiktok. Kh\u00f4ng m\u00e1y m\u00f3c c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3, kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t v\u1ec7 sinh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed9n ra t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng h\u0169 kem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201ckem c\u1ed1t th\u00e1i\u201d, kem tr\u1eafng x3, x10 trong khi \u0111\u00f3 to\u00e0n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, ch\u1ea5t l\u1ed9t t\u1ea9y, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 corticoid th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bao b\u00ec s\u01a1 s\u00e0i: S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng trong nh\u1eefng h\u0169 nh\u1ef1a \u1ecdp \u1eb9p \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 b\u1ecbch nilon. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tem nh\u00e3n, NSX\/HSD.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3m quan b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng: m\u00f9i n\u1ed3ng n\u1eb7c nh\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc hoa r\u1ebb ti\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c m\u00f9i \u201cthu\u1ed1c\u201d, ch\u1ea5t kem \u0111\u1eb7c b\u1ebft, d\u1ec5 t\u00e1ch l\u1edbp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e1n h\u00e0ng s\u01a1 s\u00e0i: Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tr\u1ed9n, mix kem ho\u1eb7c quay video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u1edbi m\u00e1c \u201ckem c\u00f4ng ty\u201d &#8211; th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 thu\u00ea nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y c\u00f2n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u201ctr\u1ed9n\u201d v\u1eabn y nguy\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n: h\u1ee9a tr\u1eafng, m\u1edd n\u00e1m, h\u1ebft m\u1ee5n trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, cam k\u1ebft d\u00f9ng cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c: \u0111\u1eb9p nhanh l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 da m\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ecf, d\u1ec5 r\u00e1t; ng\u01b0ng b\u00f4i th\u00ec b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00f4i l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi d\u1ecbu (bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n da nghi\u1ec7n corticoid)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-ban-voi-mac-%e2%80%9chang-chinh-hang%e2%80%9d-%e2%80%9chang-xach-tay%e2%80%9d-nhung-la-gia\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u00e1c \u201ch\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng\u201d \u201ch\u00e0ng x\u00e1ch tay\u201d nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7892\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7892\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7892 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-8.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t \" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-8.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-8-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-8-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-8-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7892\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 b\u00e1n l\u1ebb n\u1ed5i l\u00ean v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00e1n tr\u00ean m\u1ed7i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. Tr\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u00e0n TM\u0110T c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00f4i khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u00e3n h\u00e0ng x\u00e1ch tay gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda c\u00f3 khi l\u00e0 \u2153 gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e3n h\u00e0ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt chi ph\u00ed nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf? Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua th\u00ec ham r\u1ebb, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n th\u00ec v\u00f4 t\u00e2m, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1i m\u00e1c b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i gi\u1ed1ng \u201ch\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng\u201d l\u00e0 xu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n mua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 b\u1ecf nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u1edf b\u00ean trong.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y:<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb qu\u00e1 n\u1eeda so v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9ng th\u00f4ng tin h\u00e0ng x\u00e1ch tay c\u00f3 bill, h\u00e0ng xu\u1ea5t x\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n b\u1ea1ch cho vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bao b\u00ec c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1 so v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng (font ch\u1eef, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed in m\u00e3, m\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch,&#8230;)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ea5t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1, kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng (m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u, m\u00f9i h\u01b0\u01a1ng)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"san-pham-thuoc-boi-corticoid-ke-don\"><\/span><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i corticoid k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1eeb s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng l\u1eadu tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ec7nh b\u1ecb nghi\u1ec7n corticoid do thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh ng\u1ea1ch.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng trong n\u1ec1n d\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9m Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n tr\u00e0n lan kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi b\u00f4i th\u1ea5y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh th\u00ec t\u1ef1 \u00fd d\u00f9ng sai, d\u00f9ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7893\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7893\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7893 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-9.webp\" alt=\"Danh s\u00e1ch thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ch\u1ee9a Corticoid\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-9.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-9-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-9-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-9-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7893\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Danh s\u00e1ch thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ch\u1ee9a Corticoid ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i c\u00f3 corticoid ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam:\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Fucicort: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Betamethasone + Fusidic acid (kh\u00e1ng sinh).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Fucidin H:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Ch\u1ee9a <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Acid fusidic + Hydrocortison acetat\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Flucinar: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Fluocinolone.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Eumovate: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Clobetasone butyrate (c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 trung b\u00ecnh).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Elocon: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Mometasone furoate (trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Dermovate: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Clobetasol propionate (r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Gentrisone: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Gentamicin (kh\u00e1ng sinh) + Betamethasone (corticoid) + Clotrimazole (kh\u00e1ng n\u1ea5m).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Danh s\u00e1ch tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9. Thu\u1ed1c ch\u1ee9a corticoid kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea5u, l\u01b0u \u00fd b\u00f4i theo \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">T\u00ecm c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 t\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1eb1ng\u00a0<strong class=\"Yjhzub\" data-processed=\"true\">-sone, -olone, -solone<\/strong>\u00a0trong m\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Betamethasone (valerate, dipropionate)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Dexamethasone<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Prednisone, Prednisolone<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Methylprednisolone<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Hydrocortisone\u00a0(acetate)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Triamcinolone (acetonide)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Fluocinolone\u00a0(acetonide)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Fluticasone<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" data-processed=\"true\">Budesonide (\u00edt ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn h\u01a1n)<\/span><span class=\"uJ19be notranslate\" data-wiz-uids=\"FfXiLe_2k,FfXiLe_2l,FfXiLe_2m\" data-processed=\"true\"><span class=\"vKEkVd\" data-animation-atomic=\"\" data-wiz-attrbind=\"class=FfXiLe_2k\/TKHnVd;\" data-processed=\"true\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nen-lam-gi-khi-phat-hien-da-nhiem-corticoid\"><\/span><b>N\u00ean l\u00e0m g\u00ec khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7894\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7894\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7894 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-10.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c corticoid\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-10.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-10-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-10-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-10-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7894\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c corticoid c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a corticoid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i corticoid m\u1ea1nh, v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. C\u00e1ch ng\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p theo t\u1eebng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <\/span><b>th\u0103m kh\u00e1m b\u1edfi b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean l\u01b0u truy\u1ec1n, l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng, peel da ho\u1eb7c treatment m\u1ea1nh \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Song song \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7n t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, tr\u00e1nh trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, tr\u00e1nh n\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7895\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7895\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7895 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-11.webp\" alt=\"th\u0103m kh\u00e1m da li\u1ec5u\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-11.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-11-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-11-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-11-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7895\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 khi c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-phuong-phap-dieu-tri-da-nhiem-corticoid-chuyen-nghiep\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i, c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa y khoa v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. T\u00f9y m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9, b\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3m li\u1ec1u corticoid t\u1eeb t\u1eeb, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam kh\u00f4ng steroid, thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng sinh h\u1ecdc, laser m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec7n di ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf chuy\u00ean khoa v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p nhanh, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 <\/span><b>kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng sinh l\u00fd b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a da<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t. V\u1eady n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb k\u00e9o d\u00e0i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng th\u00e1ng) v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129 ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-tai-nha-khi-dieu-tri-da-nhiem-corticoid\"><\/span><b>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 khi \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Da c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kinh t\u1ebf eo h\u1eb9p, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i theo \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da li\u1ec5u th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng &#8220;d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m&#8221; uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1eebng n\u00ean ham r\u1ebb v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng tr\u00f4i n\u1ed5i thi\u1ebfu ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-duong-phuc-hoi-thai-doc-da-gsc\/\">Xem ngay: Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i chuy\u00ean cho da nhi\u1ec5m cort<\/a><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7903\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7903\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7903 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-12-2.webp\" alt=\"Vi\u1ec7c che ch\u1eafn ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng khi da y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-12-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-12-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-12-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Corticoid-12-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7903\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vi\u1ec7c che ch\u1eafn ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng khi da y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi da b\u1ecb l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c cortiocoid th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c, \u01b0u ti\u00ean kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, che ch\u1eafn v\u1eadt l\u00fd khi ra ngo\u00e0i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec5m corticoid c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn, tr\u00e1nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quay l\u1ea1i th\u00f3i quen l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p nhanh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u0169 Th\u1ecb Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, D., Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb Minh, P., \u0110\u1ed7 Th\u1ecb Thu, H., \u0110\u00e0o Tr\u1ecdng, K., &amp; L\u00ea H\u1eefu, D. (2024). \u0110\u1eb6C \u0110I\u1ec2M L\u00c2M S\u00c0NG V\u00c0 M\u1ed8T S\u1ed0 Y\u1ebeU T\u1ed0 LI\u00caN QUAN C\u1ee6A B\u1ec6NH TR\u1ee8NG C\u00c1 TH\u00d4NG TH\u01af\u1edcNG M\u1ee8C \u0110\u1ed8 TRUNG B\u00ccNH \u2013 N\u1eb6NG T\u1ea0I B\u1ec6NH VI\u1ec6N DA LI\u1ec4U TRUNG \u01af\u01a0NG. T\u1ea1p Ch\u00ed Da Li\u1ec5u H\u1ecdc Vi\u1ec7t Nam, 44. <a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.56320\/tcdlhvn.44.157\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.56320\/tcdlhvn.44.157<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Topical steroids (corticosteroid creams). (2023, October 26). DermNet\u00ae. <a href=\"https:\/\/dermnetnz.org\/topics\/topical-steroid?utm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/dermnetnz.org\/topics\/topical-steroid?utm<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Da nhi\u1ec5m corticoid l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da do l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng corticoid trong thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00eau r\u00f5 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da n\u00e0y<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7885,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7884","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7884","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7884"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7884\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7937,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7884\/revisions\/7937"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7885"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7884"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7884"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7884"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}